  "texts": [
    "• Instructions for the LLM: These are provided by the educator and are explained in Section III B.",
    "• Complexity: By default, the complexity of the feedback is set to medium, but students have the option to change it to low or high based on their needs.",
    "The specific prompts given to the LLM for each complexity level are as follows:",
    "-\"Low\" instructs the LLM to \"Write a very easy to understand feedback in five sentences for a secondary school student\".",
    "-\"Middle\" instructs it to \"Write your feedback for a high school student\"."
  ],
